title: Gunbound Original Soundtrack
description:

File Size = 32.4 MB
Album Length = 45 minutes, 22 seconds
Format = VBR MP3 @ 8-128kbps 22kHz for the original tracks and 32-96kbps 44kHz for the newer songs
